<Link id="l00242" /><CodeLine lineNumber="242"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00243" /><CodeLine lineNumber="243"><Highlight kind="comment">/// An advisor plugin adds a new advisor at runtime by registering an instance</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00244" /><CodeLine lineNumber="244"><Highlight kind="comment">/// of PluginInlineAdvisorAnalysis in the current ModuleAnalysisManager.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00245" /><CodeLine lineNumber="245"><Highlight kind="comment">/// For example, the following code dynamically registers a</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00246" /><CodeLine lineNumber="246"><Highlight kind="comment">/// DefaultInlineAdvisor:</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00250" /><CodeLine lineNumber="250"><Highlight kind="comment">/// InlineAdvisor &#42;defaultAdvisorFactory(Module &amp;M,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00251" /><CodeLine lineNumber="251"><Highlight kind="comment">///                                      FunctionAnalysisManager &amp;FAM,</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00254" /><CodeLine lineNumber="254"><Highlight kind="comment">///   return new DefaultInlineAdvisor(M, FAM, Params, IC);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00255" /><CodeLine lineNumber="255"><Highlight kind="comment">/// &#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00256" /><CodeLine lineNumber="256"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00257" /><CodeLine lineNumber="257"><Highlight kind="comment">/// &#125; // namespace</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00258" /><CodeLine lineNumber="258"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00259" /><CodeLine lineNumber="259"><Highlight kind="comment">/// extern &quot;C&quot; LLVM&#95;ATTRIBUTE&#95;WEAK ::llvm::PassPluginLibraryInfo</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00260" /><CodeLine lineNumber="260"><Highlight kind="comment">/// llvmGetPassPluginInfo() &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00261" /><CodeLine lineNumber="261"><Highlight kind="comment">///   return &#123;LLVM&#95;PLUGIN&#95;API&#95;VERSION, &quot;DynamicDefaultAdvisor&quot;,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00262" /><CodeLine lineNumber="262"><Highlight kind="comment">///           LLVM&#95;VERSION&#95;STRING,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00263" /><CodeLine lineNumber="263"><Highlight kind="comment">///           &#91;&#93;(PassBuilder &amp;PB) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00268" /><CodeLine lineNumber="268"><Highlight kind="comment">///                 &#125;);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00269" /><CodeLine lineNumber="269"><Highlight kind="comment">///           &#125;&#125;;</Highlight></CodeLine>
